te Foundation and led the 2015 Paris Accords on climate targets.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1980, \"end\": 2007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Climate_Foundation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European Climate Foundation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Climate_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Climate_Foundation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ms Tubiana\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2015 Paris Accords\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"climate targets\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is also a former adviser to former Socialist President Fran\\u00e7ois Hollande and last week she signed an open letter from 70 intellectuals urging the NFP to work immediately with others to form a broad-based \\\"republican programme and government\\\".\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fran\\u00e7ois_Hollande\", \"score\": 0.999999987528554, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fran\\u00e7ois Hollande\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fran\\u00e7ois_Hollande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fran\\u00e7ois_Hollande\"}, {\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\", \"score\": 0.9932556778913609, \"rank\": 0.00679004200326512, \"text\": \"NFP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Federation_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republicanism\", \"score\": 0.9999995778158318, \"rank\": 2.0713812676204393e-07, \"